                                "stop": 13.847,
                                "byte_start": 100552,
                                "byte_stop": 156036,
                                "text": "The judgment and opinion of the Court in 75-1278, Mt. Healthy School District against Doyle will be announced by Mr. Justice Rehnquist."
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "start": 13.847,
                        "stop": 149.539,
